name: Goku Vs Naruto
description:
This is a game where you have to kill Goku or Naruto, you
 can be Goku or Naruto, it was made by a 10-year-old creator
 with Goku you have 2 attacks that are with the left click
 of the mouse sticks and with the right throws gusts of ki
 Naruto It only has one attack but it is the strongest one that
 runs with the left click of the mouse that is a knife
